description_text:
Good morning,


I hope you're doing well! My name is Manu, and I run Manuatures, an
Instagram page focused on hobbies, and tech reviews, with a strong and
engaged audience of over 20K followers across Europe and North America.


I’d love the opportunity to review and showcase your products to my
audience. My Instagram reaches around 100K users monthly, and I focus on
creating engaging posts.


Please let me know if you’d be open to collaborating—I’d be happy to
discuss details.


Looking forward to your thoughts!.



https://www.instagram.com/manuatures/


Best regards,

Manu

Creator of Manuatures
